  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Guests can enjoy a continental breakfast buffet with freshly-made pastries, cold meats, cheeses and cereals.</p>
<p>Restaurant Ripa Relais has a warm and cosy ambience with exposed brick arches and wooden beams. The menu changes seasonally and dishes are based on traditional Umbrian cuisine with a modern twist, using local ingredients and olive oil made from the trees on the hotel grounds.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <cateringShortDescription></cateringShortDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>1</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>Ripa Relais has a very peaceful location in the <a data-udi="umb://document/15ea075a2eaf4537b6a6f77597d59053" href="/{localLink:umb://document/15ea075a2eaf4537b6a6f77597d59053}" title="Umbria">Umbrian</a> countryside. There’s only 16 rooms here too so you’re almost guaranteed a relaxing holiday. The rooms are all spread out throughout the grounds in four ancient farm buildings that have been restored to create a comfy space. Expect wrought-iron beds, wooden beams and locally-made furniture.</p>
<p>The gardens are very well maintained and they’re a lovely spot to just sit and enjoy the views. There’s a pool here too so you can cool off if it gets warm. The spa is a lovely facility so try and spend a couple of hours here if you can – there’s a whirlpool, sauna and steam room. We love the restaurant here, it has some amazing Umbrian food to try. The menu changes seasonally to make the most of locally-sourced ingredients – expect to see truffles, local cheese, beef sourced from <a data-udi="umb://document/58d85ec0faa548b2ab580143fdc9b722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/58d85ec0faa548b2ab580143fdc9b722}" title="Tuscany &amp; Umbria">Tuscany</a> and olive oil made from the hotel’s own trees.</p>
<p>We recommend hiring a car when you stay here so you can get out and about to explore Umbria. The region’s capital, Perugia, is only a half an hour’s drive away and Assisi is only 20 minutes.</p>
<p>Car hire is recommended for this hotel. SINA Brufani is approx. 2 hours 15 mins from Rome airport</p>]]></description>
