  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool</strong></span></p>
<p>The large pool is surrounded by peaceful gardens and has a hydro massage corner. A pool bar offers light lunches, snacks and ice cream. It’s open from May to September.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Spa</strong></span></p>
<p>Ripa Relais spa is well equipped with sauna, Turkish bath, whirlpool and relaxation area. Entrance to the spa, beauty treatments and massages are payable locally.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Free mountain bike rental</li>
<li>Onsite parking</li>
<li>Free WiFi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
