  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> are finished in a classic style with terracotta floors, wooden furniture and wrought iron beds. They measure 15-17m² and can sleep up to two adults. Facilities include air conditioning, minibar, TV, free WiFi and hairdryer.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> offer more space with 20-25m² and can accommodate up to three adults.</p>
<p><strong>Classic Rooms for Single Use </strong>are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
